 "qrT", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "An ear-ring,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ear-drop;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "i. q."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$anofN", "text_ar": "شَنْفٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (K:) or the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "thing that is suspended to the lobe of the ear;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Mgh, Msb, K, TA;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "such as a silver bead fashioned like a pearl, or a pendant of gold;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$nf", "text_ar": "شنف"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "being that which is in the upper part of the ear: (TA:) pl. [of pauc.]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aqoriTapN", "text_ar": "اَقْرِطَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh, Msb) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aqoraATN", "text_ar": "اَقْرَاطٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) and [of mult.]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qiraTapN", "text_ar": "قِرَطَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Mgh, Msb, K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qiraATN", "text_ar": "قِرَاطٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "quruwTN", "text_ar": "قُرُوطٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (K.) It is said in a proverb,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "xu*ohu walawo biquroTaY maAriyapa", "text_ar": "خُذْهُ وَلَوْ بِقُرْطَى مَارِيَةَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Take thou it, although by means of"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "giving for it"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the two earrings of Máriyeh"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; (TA, S, K, in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mrY", "text_ar": "مرى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ";) i. e., take thou it at all events: (K in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mrY", "text_ar": "مرى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ":) this Máriyeh, respecting whom authors differ, was the first Arab woman who wore ear-rings, and her ear-rings are said to have been of great value. (TA.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlquroTu", "text_ar": "القُرْطُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The Pleiades"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Alv~uray~aA", "text_ar": "الثُّرَيَّا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "): so called by way of comparison. (TA.)       -A2-"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A certain plant, like the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ruTubap", "text_ar": "رُطُبَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "raTobap", "text_ar": "رَطْبَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a species of trefoil,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "clover"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "],"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "except that it is superior in size,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "quality, to the latter,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AHn, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and larger in the leaves, fed upon by horses and the like;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AHn, TA;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in Persian"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$abo*ar", "text_ar": "شَبْذَر"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$abodar", "text_ar": "شَبْدَر"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (AHn, K.) [See"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "birosiymN", "text_ar": "بِرْسِيمٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".]"}], "source_refs": ["K", "TA", "Mgh", "Msb", "S", "AHn"]}, {"entry_id": "n42601", "headword_ar": "قُرْطٌ", "root": "qrT", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ": see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qiraATN", "text_ar": "قِرَاطٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "."}], "source_refs": []}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark